title: Hatsune Miku Project Mirai DX
description: This is the complete soundtrack to the Nintendo 3DS game, Hatsune Miku Project Mirai DX. It includes every track that is playable in-game, as well as room themes and menu themes. Each song has been translated to its English title, and each title also includes the name of the character featured in the song, if any. This took a very long time to hand-edit and I hope you enjoy this album!
